messages.content: I've not made it to Bali yet. Have spent a lot of time in India and I'm about to go to the Himalayas. I'd love to take my son to Bali one day

Hi Carina,

Thank you for such a lovely message. I've not seen your work before, and really like it, so I went on your website, and love it. I have to say I see so much underwhelming jewellery around , and I love what you're putting out there. It's important to have a distinct voice. 

How is it going for you? 

I'm transitioning to fine and I've given myself a 2 year window . It's not a long term thing really to sell gold plated jewellery ... you have to sell so much. 

Do you do wholesale?

Loren hey! Ive followed your work for a long time and love the character in every piece and your love letter emails too. I finally saw your jewelry in person at poet and the bench last fall. 
Waving hello from across the Internet in Bali. 
Love to you, Carina
